The paper focuses on the co-design of control and communication systems for distributed self-triggered control over wireless multi-hop networks. This topic falls under the intersection of several CS sub-disciplines, including control systems (cs.SY), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), robotics (cs.RO), and information theory (cs.IT). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
